const dark = {
        title: 'dark',
        colors:{
            primary: 'hsl(232, 19%, 15%)',
            background: 'hsl(207, 26%, 17%)',
            cardBackground: 'hsl(228, 28%, 20%)',
            cardHover: '#333a56',
            textBlue: 'hsl(228, 34%, 66%)',
            text: '#fff',
            upColor: 'hsl(163, 72%, 41%)',
            downColor: 'hsl(356, 69%, 56%)',
            filter: 'invert(100%)',
    }
}
export default dark
